data.description: Character and craftsmanship abounds this beautiful 18th century Victorian home in the historical community of Ellwood City.  This corner lot location offers curb appeal from all angles. Starting with the detail of the mosaic tile on the large front porch, or walking in to luxurious marble tile in either entrance. The C3 commercial zoning, along with the large dining room, formal living room, and sitting areas throughout the house make this the perfect destination for your future bed & breakfast. Or you can move the entire family in! With plenty room for growth & equity, this is the perfect investor/handyman special Being sold in "as is" condition.
